OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,FMillions of workers are set to benefit
OL,7,Ffrom new legal rights which mean they
OL,8,Fcan request flexible working from
OL,9,Ftheir first day at a new job, ITV
OL,10,FNews' Sangeeta Kandola has more
OL,12,FNew rights to request flexible working
OL,13,Fshould benefit millions of workers,
OL,14,Faccording to workplace experts.
OL,16,FFrom Saturday, employees will have the
OL,17,Flegal right to request flexible
OL,18,Fworking from their first day in a new
OL,19,Fjob. Previously, it only applied if
OL,20,Fsomeone had worked for their employer
OL,21,Ffor 26 weeks or more.
