OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,FPeter Cheese, chief executive of the
OL,7,FChartered Institute of Personnel and
OL,8,FDevelopment (CIPD), said: "This new
OL,9,Fday one right stands to benefit
OL,10,Fmillions of people, helping them to
OL,11,Fbalance their work and life
OL,12,Fcommitments and give them more say and
OL,13,Fmore opportunity in where and how they
OL,14,Fwork.
