OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,F"Flexibility around time, scheduling
OL,7,Fand place of work can be
OL,8,Ftransformative in opening up
OL,9,Fopportunities for people to get into
OL,10,Fand stay in work, especially those who
OL,11,Fhave health conditions, caring
OL,12,Fresponsibilities, or other life
OL,13,Fchoices they want to make.
OL,15,F"With an ageing population, and rising
OL,16,Flevels of economically inactive people
OL,17,Fdue to ill health, flexible working is
OL,18,Fmore important than ever, and has been
OL,19,Fshown to support better wellbeing,
OL,20,Fmaking it good for individuals as well
OL,21,Fas organisations.
