OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,FIts chief executive, Susan Clews,
OL,7,Fsaid: "There has been a global shift
OL,8,Fto flexible working following the
OL,9,Fpandemic, which has allowed more
OL,10,Fpeople to better balance their working
OL,11,Flives and employers have also
OL,12,Fbenefited from being an attractive
OL,13,Fplace to work.
OL,15,F"Our new code aims to foster flexible
OL,16,Fworking further and covers the new law
OL,17,Fchanges. It sets out good practice on
OL,18,Fflexible working requests and will
OL,19,Fhelp employers and employees avoid any
OL,20,Fpitfalls.
