OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,F"There are many types of flexible
OL,7,Fworking such as part-time working,
OL,8,Fflexitime, job sharing, staggered
OL,9,Fhours, hybrid and homeworking. The
OL,10,Fstarting position for businesses
OL,11,Fshould be to consider what may be
OL,12,Fpossible."
OL,14,FA study of 4,000 workers by campaign
OL,15,Fgroup Timewise found that half would
OL,16,Fconsider asking for a flexible pattern
OL,17,Fof work using the day one right to
OL,18,Frequest in a new job.
