OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,FChief executive Claire Campbell said:
OL,7,F"The new legislation will help job
OL,8,Fhunters feel entitled to ask about
OL,9,Fflexible working options and requests
OL,10,Fcould start coming thick and fast.
OL,12,F"Flexible working and diversity and
OL,13,Finclusion are interwoven, and
OL,14,Fbusinesses that make the most of the
OL,15,Fopportunity could really open some
OL,16,Fdoors to new and exciting talent."
OL,18,FResearch by campaign group Pregnant
OL,19,FThen Screwed found that mothers are
OL,20,Ftwice as likely as fathers to ask for
OL,21,Fflexible working after parental leave.
